reviewText: I chose this video because I grew up exercising with the Jack LaLanne show as part of a morning routine when I was growing up.  I purchased it as a gift because I know a couple who attend water aerobic classes and would be an interest for them since they too watched the Jack LaLanne Show many years ago.  This video is not a disappointment at all.  Its great.  The price was right and the vendor shipped it to me immediately.  The video arrived ahead of schedule and was in perfect condition.
